imdb.plot outline: Have you ever fallen asleep while someone was playing with your hair? Well let your hair down and relax with these ASMR hair brushing videos that feature brushing, tapping, whispering, and visual relaxation techniques. We will show you how to give the most relaxing scalp massages that are sure to have you snoozing.
